# ==============================================================

# --- Supabase ---
# Všetko nájdeš v: Supabase Dashboard → tvoj projekt → Settings (ikona ozubeného kolesa) → API
#
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL
#   V Supabase: Settings → API → "Project URL"
#   Skopíruj celú URL (napr. https://xxxx.supabase.co)
#
# VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID
#   V Supabase: Settings → API → "Project ID" (pod Project URL)
#   Alebo z Project URL: časť pred .supabase.co (napr. xxxx)
#
# VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY
#   V Supabase: Settings → API → "Project API keys" → kľúč s názvom "anon" / "public"
#   Používaj len anon (public) kľúč – NIKDY service_role key tu ani vo Vercel
#
VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=your-anon-public-key

# Voliteľné pre CLI (migrácie a supabase link/push):
# SUPABASE_DB_URL=postgresql://postgres:HESLO@db.XXXX.supabase.co:5432/postgres
# SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN=token z Supabase Dashboard → Account → Access Tokens

# --- Firebase (voliteľné – ak sú nastavené, auth sa rieši cez Firebase) ---
# Firebase Console → Project Settings → General → Your apps → Web app
# V Supabase treba povoliť Third-Party Auth (Firebase) a nastaviť project_id.
# V Firebase treba používateľom nastaviť custom claim: role = 'authenticated'
# Více: docs/FIREBASE-AUTH-SETUP.md
# VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=
# VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=
# VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=
# VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=

# ==============================================================
# POZNÁMKY:
# - Nikdy nepridávaj VITE_SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY do .env!
#   Service role key patrí iba do Supabase edge function secrets.
